            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1407159714,
            "creation_date": 1407159714,
            "body": "<p>Got myself on this situation this morning... This was my code to run at midnight<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    scheduler = Executors.newScheduledThreadPool(1);\n    Long midnight=LocalDateTime.now().until(LocalDate.now().plusDays(1).atStartOfDay(), ChronoUnit.MINUTES);\n    scheduler.scheduleAtFixedRate(this, midnight, 1440,  TimeUnit.MINUTES);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 25120113,
            "question_id": 8066141
        },
        {
            "owner": {
