            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1320847604,
            "creation_date": 1320847604,
            "body": "<p>Check out <a href=\"http://www.quartz-scheduler.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quartz<\/a>. We use it for our production apps, and it's very good. It works pretty much like crontab. You can specify a time during a set schedule and it'll execute a callback at that time.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 8066197,
